title: Jets GM Shakeup, Fatal Flaws with Andrew Perloff (Football 5/16)
description:
Will Brinson and Andrew Perloff of the Dan Patrick Show break down the latest news out of New York, take a look at the Broncos quarterback situation, discuss how the Redskins should handle their young QB, run around the NFL news cycle, rank the regular Pick Six Podcast contributors (!) and chat about Game of Thrones.
